thread.title: Jeannine

author: Jeannine
title: Jeannine
text: A friend showed me her folder just days before our first dress rehearsal. I was able to order the folder on Friday and receive it Tuesday. The strap on the back of the folder allowed one hand to steady it while another strap across the bottom kept the large score from falling off. There are multiple other handy helps - a removable part that makes it a three-ring binder and 12 strings for holding sheet music. It's high quality and I'm confident it can be used for many, many years.
